The workspace is using a rigid hierarchy with applications owning services. If you have instances where a service is not owned by a application please document it under[Shared Services](comp://undefined/). This is a temporary repository until we define a new architecture model to better reflect current development.

  
If you are documenting new changes or apps, please remember to include the dependencies **FROM** known requirements which you are satisfying and **TO** the infrastructure you are deploying to.Direction is key for maintaining an overview.
